  <div class="markdown max-w-xl">
    <p>Valinor Earth focuses on leveraging Technology to help Farmers lead better, happier lives. We help farmers increase their incomes by educating them, helping them with the right seeds, augment them with better and optimized agricultural practices.</p>
    <p>Valinor Earth is instrumental in cross-pollinating technical innovations across regions. Right now, we are introducing many innovative Japanese technologies, best practices, and methodologies to India and other Asian countries.</p>
    <p>In India, Valinor Earth is working closely with the Government bodies from Agriculture Departments of various States and Union Territories to help farmers with easy-to-access credit. We leverage satellite imagery and our proprietory soil sampling technology to calculate a farmland's NDVI (Normalized Difference Vegetation Index) and help the farmers and interested parties to find the optimal time to harvest their crops.</p>
